Class MockBulkClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xbib.elasticsearch.support.client.AbstractClient

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientFactory, DocumentIngest, Ingest

    public class MockBulkClient
extends BulkClient
implements Ingest
    Mock client for Bulk API. Do not perform actions on a real cluster. Useful for testing or dry runs.
